Text: what would it take to get you to upload his other stuff?

at sikbatman:  Funny you should ask, he has several albums avaliable on his website, but this is like the only complete album I have seen posted.  I mean you can always find fragments of his stuff out there, but nothing complete.  So to answer your question: I would if i could, but I can't because I have nothing else by him.  Good luck with that! : )
